          "TaskCard.asComponent"
        ],
        "brandReviewed": false,
        "a11yReviewed": false,
        "notes": "Tappable row for a patient task. Composes Avatar (sm) + name + meta + trailing chevron / circle-check. State drives the modifier class (.task-card-overdue / -in-progress / -completed) and the trailing-icon glyph. For state='overdue', an 'Overdue' badge auto-prepends the meta text. For state='in-progress', the meta picks up teal coloring via the `.task-card-in-progress .task-card-meta` descendant rule (no inline style). For state='completed', the card renders as a non-interactive <div>, ignoring href / asComponent. Otherwise: asComponent prop accepts a caller-supplied component (router-Link); href falls back to plain <a>; neither falls back to presentational <div>."
      }
    },
