        "brandReviewed": true,
        "a11yReviewed": true,
        "notes": "THE HERO COMPONENT for cc-02 thread panel. Variants: standard (sand surface, primary-500 left), is-urgent (red surface + dividers), is-warning (amber surface + dividers — semantic warning use of amber per DESIGN.md §Tag-semantic), is-historical (read-only opacity-70, no actions). Sections (summary, effects, attachment, actions, note) individually optional. Header h3 uses Lora (display) per DESIGN.md §Typography. Root is <section role='region' aria-labelledby> with <h3 id> for landmark navigation. noteMode ('hidden'|'optional'|'required') drives textarea disclosure tied to parent's reject/approve flow; noteRef forwards focus for the Reject intent flow. attachment.viewed=false applies the .thread-approval-attachment-unviewed warning class (silent-failure prevention per IA review). Action buttons are caller-supplied via actions slot using bare <button class='btn-primary btn-sm'> + <button class='btn-outline btn-sm'> per PL exemplar. Brand-fidelity + IA + a11y review (3-expert panel, 2026-04-24) all returned 'iterate'; iterate pass shipped in same Patch B."
